            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1700644857816-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, remove the pan from the heat and stir in your <strong>clotted cream </strong>– this is your<strong> butter chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
